{"tid":1704151,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聽日大三罷之前 我作為一個香港人有說話想同大家講","createTime":"2019-11-10T14:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T17:31:52.000Z","uid":113368,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a451ca6a4122d08f1e8505260da89bd0308f5c0","tid":1704151,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:50:29.000Z","msg":"本人係一名NBA死忠 如果你同我一樣有睇開NBA既 你應該會知道作為曾經既籃球霸權 勇士 因為主力全傷 最近開季2勝8負 勇士既總教練Steve Kerr被問到對於自己球隊咁不像樣既開季成績既看法既時候 佢講左一句說話 而我覺得呢句說話 更適合講俾香港人聽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「我們不應該接受我們的命運，不應該為自己感到抱歉</strong></span></span>，或者要等待樂透選秀這種鬼話，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我們應該贏下更多比賽</strong></span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x1oSVvK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx1oSVvK.png&h=d324ffa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實人生在世不如意事 實在係十常八九 你冇可能一直都贏 一定會遇到一些挫折 亦會有失去既東西 16歲女童的貞節 手腳 眼 周同學 甚至乎 咁多位義士既生命 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你會感到抱歉<br />\n你會感到氣餒<br />\n你會感到冇力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但 <br />\n你不可以放棄<br />\n你不可以習慣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你不可以接受這個不公的命運<br />\n你不可以向命運低頭</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我不懂文學 不懂措辭語句<br />\n但如果香港係一支球隊既話<br />\n不論強或弱<br />\n我一直都會以香港為榮<br />\n以香港人的身份為榮<br />\n你在香港你就會感受到最高質素的巿民<br />\n大家都只有一個要求<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你可以輸<br />\n你可以做得唔好<br />\n但是<br />\n你必須讓我們看到你想贏既心</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝各位香港人武運亨通<br />\n明天馬路再聚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n煲底相見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3hS4MMm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3hS4MMm.jpg&h=0ad8b1cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"801869065d2bdfa05d25989a41c596ac119c8c75","tid":1704151,"uid":303052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OnrdE5P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOnrdE5P.gif&h=be3be017&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"509866a3a57c96a33c05959bd2057ec1a53a56a0","tid":1704151,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jM9yEVS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjM9yEVS.gif&h=36baf129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"caaf1ed3187ca9f8bed8a46672afd121610c2004","tid":1704151,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:52:34.000Z","msg":"我唔識講 你輸唔緊要 冇可能次次都贏 但<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你要有想贏 想反抗命運既心</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3f041f6847d8721f97fb07c6adbbd58590abdcfe","tid":1704151,"uid":113368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:53:28.000Z","msg":"希望聽日可以係馬路見到大家"},{"pid":"bab7446d2d49bb74a691fbf6e69464d21d22b31c","tid":1704151,"uid":113368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"不應為自己感到抱歉"},{"pid":"186e7cd04a13d7430f19b9d4e884e7c473b08bca","tid":1704151,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"雙十一 周圍塞 上晝七點遍地開花 塞佢老母 真正攬炒<br />\n阻鳩交通變相全民罷工 每一個人都要出黎<br />\n<br />\n7AM｛黎明行動｝推到聽朝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n-<br />\n雙十一，周圍塞，阻塞交通變相全民罷工 悼念完一定要有行動，手足既血不可白流<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703687</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n「黎明行動」低風險新職業 - 扮工師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703696</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【召集和理非】聽朝7點唔知點做好？入嚟睇下有咩最簡單嘅嘢可以做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703752</a>